Problem-86. Partition List
Difficulty-Medium
Platform-Leetcode
Approach-Method Used: Two dummy nodes + single traversal
Create two lists:
small → nodes < x
greater → nodes >= x
Traverse the list once and attach nodes accordingly.
Set grea.next = null (to avoid cycle).
Connect small list to greater list.
Return small.next.
Time: O(n)
Space: O(1)
Solution-
class Solution {
    public ListNode partition(ListNode head, int x) {
        ListNode small=new ListNode(0);
        ListNode greater=new ListNode(0);
        ListNode sma=small;
        ListNode grea=greater;
        while(head!=null){
            if(head.val<x){
                sma.next=head;
                sma=sma.next;
            }
            else{
                grea.next=head;
                grea=grea.next;
            }
            head=head.next;
        }
        grea.next=null;
        sma.next=greater.next;
        return small.next;
    }
}
